guide.title: My Bids Guide
guide.content: This page tracks every job you have bid on. Use the filter to see jobs with a specific status.
guide.biddedDesc: You have placed a bid, but the job is still open for other installers to bid on.
guide.awardedDesc: Congratulations! The Job Giver has selected you. You must accept the job to proceed.
guide.inProgressDesc: You have accepted the job and can now communicate with the Job Giver.
guide.completedDesc: The job is finished and you have been paid. You'll see any reputation points you earned here.
guide.notSelectedDesc: The Job Giver chose another installer for this project.
